  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We implemented the SHAP analysis using the open-source python package according to the documentation (Lundberg and Lee, 2021).",
    "For clinical validation, we analyzed 5,000 patients from the validation data for each model.",
    "In order to understand which features had the greatest influence on disease prediction at the population level, we summed the SHAP scores and examined the top clinical features (diagnoses, procedures, observations/values, medications).",
    "We chose this measure because it accounts for the magnitude of the effect of a feature as well as its prevalence in the population.",
    "SHAP values are additive, so this metric represents the overall contribution of a feature to the prediction of disease within the population."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "We implemented the SHAP analysis using the open-source python package according to the documentation (Lundberg and Lee, 2021)."
  ]
}